@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Browse Books
skinparam style strictuml

/' TEXT DESCRIPTION (Steps)
1. Member opens the catalog page.
2. Member enters keywords/filters.
3. System validates input.
4. System searches the catalog.
5. If results exist, system displays the list; otherwise shows "No results".
6. Member either selects a book to view details or ends browsing.
'/

start
:Open catalog page;
:Enter keywords/filters;
if (Input valid?) then (Yes)
  :Search catalog;
  if (Results found?) then (Yes)
    :Display results list;
  else (No)
    :Display "No results";
  endif
  :Select a book or end browsing;
else (No)
  :Show validation error;
endif
stop

@enduml